parameters:
Innkeeper: Have you entered the auction venue? Well, if you
don't have any money, it's just a big building.

Innkeeper: Welcome to the Fotizona Port! You can enjoy wines
from all over the empire here!

Traveling Art Merchant: Dealing with nobles can be
exhausting. I want to live a life where I can look at the
sea someday.

Burly Worker: Hahaha, look at these impressive biceps,
right? The port is the best place to train a man.

Young Worker: I heard that if I train like my older brother
and drink lots of meat and alcohol, it'll be great, but I
wonder if I can endure it?
